dataIdInfo.idPurp: This dataset was produced as part of a Phase 1 Archaeological Resource Impact Assessment for the Nova Scotia Department of Agriculture at Grand Pre Marsh (NS008). Field data is generally accurate to 3-5m, while data digitized from secondary sources expresses a harder to quantify locational error. RTK survey data accuracies are reported in each record. All data is intended to geospatially document the methods or illustrate the results of this project.
